{
  "stem": "25287.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my younger sister and me-- I don't know-- with a knife, we cut and we make by hand some slippers for her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then we get a little extra bed for [INAUDIBLE] lager sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the whole deal in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, zahlappell and standing outside till when they counting you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they missed you counting was disappear, then we needed to [? kneel. ?] And once, Elizabeth said to me we went to help to bring the food.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after, when we get to this small lager, we cut the grass and make-- cover the bunker for the German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the American people came, so took us back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we came back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People said the worst thing about-- they took you to crematory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then he can selected us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we when to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Latrine-- you know what this means, a latrine?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- but you cannot go when you needed to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Either you hold, or-- And they took our schmatta, the clothes, to-- because we have lice, I think, when we came back-- not the-- not the first couple weeks in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, and one's like-- who was with us, who gave the bread, and niece was with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw her dress, you know, so I want to tell the blockalteste [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She hit me so I still have the mark, because we was nothing on us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This one, they needed later on, operate on, in Magdeburg, but not in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because if they send you to the river, then they said they sent you to the river.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They called the first aid, and they took you to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But was a doctor, you know, in Magdeburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
